SentimentLabel: You can probably get away with not doing anything for this class but you'll understand the material more if you actually attend class . Find a way to take it while the sun is up though cause walking back to the dorms from the Art Building is kind of scary .

The workload was way too much for an intro class designed for first years . The professor herself had poor time management and was rude to students . You will need to spend a lot of time outside of class to complete projects .
